w></view><view class="strategy-item data-v-4a17e6c4"><view class="strategy-icon data-v-4a17e6c4">❤️</view><view class="strategy-name data-v-4a17e6c4">血量管理</view><view class="strategy-desc data-v-4a17e6c4">血量低时谨慎质疑，保留生存机会</view></view><view class="strategy-item data-v-4a17e6c4"><view class="strategy-icon data-v-4a17e6c4">🎯</view><view class="strategy-name data-v-4a17e6c4">诱敌深入</view><view class="strategy-desc data-v-4a17e6c4">持有大牌时故意示弱，引诱对手质疑</view></view></view></view><view class="section-block data-v-4a17e6c4"><view class="section-header data-v-4a17e6c4"><view class="section-icon data-v-4a17e6c4">🔢</view><view class="section-title data-v-4a17e6c4">数值大小</view><view class="section-sub data-v-4a17e6c4">点数排序</view></view><view class="value-order data-v-4a17e6c4"><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">2</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">3</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">4</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">5</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">6</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">7</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">8</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">9</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">10</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">J</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">Q</view><view class="value-item data-v-4a17e6c4">K</view><view class="value-item king data-v-4a17e6c4">A</view></view><view class="tip-box data-v-4a17e6c4"><text class="tip-icon data-v-4a17e6c4">✨</text><text class="tip-text data-v-4a17e6c4">A是最大的点数，可以组成A-2-3-4-5的顺子</text></view></view><view class="bottom-section data-v-4a17e6c4"><button data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['goToGame',['$event']]]]]}}" class="start-btn data-v-4a17e6c4" bindtap="__e">开始游戏</button></view></view>